{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Get ready to dive into the most absurd, unpredictable universe you've ever seen with The Great Fluctus! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Great Fluctus</strong> is a colony-building sandbox with survival elements, set in a voxel-based alien world with a truly unique visual style. Players mine resources, shape the terrain, and transform a small space base into a lively alien town. Build, farm, trade, and manage your evolving community while using diplomacy to attract new inhabitants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whenever you need a break from colony life, explore the nearby alien civilization. Trade with locals, take on quests, or even join the sacred race to deliver a baby shrimpling. The world is full of surprises, where quirky characters, humorous dialogues, and unpredictable events add depth and charm. Every encounter weaves into a lighthearted storyline, blending exploration, creativity, and strategy in this dynamic sandbox experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085280/extras/GifEmail2.gif?t=1729713921\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085280/extras/GifEmail1.gif?t=1729713921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085280/extras/gif_yellow.gif?t=1729713921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085280/extras/GifEmail3.gif?t=1729713921\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729713921","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st